MPlayer: MPlayer (MPlayer Video Player)
MPlayer:
MPlayer: MPlayer is a movie player which runs on many systems. It 
MPlayer: plays most MPEG/VOB, AVI, Ogg/OGM, VIVO, ASF/WMA/WMV, QT/MOV/MP4, 
MPlayer: RealMedia, Matroska, NUT, NuppelVideo, FLI, YUV4MPEG, FILM, RoQ, 
MPlayer: PVA files, supported by many native, XAnim, and Win32 DLL codecs. 
MPlayer: You can watch VideoCD, SVCD, DVD, 3ivx, DivX 3/4/5 and even WMV movies.
MPlayer:
MPlayer: MPlayer is available under the GNU General Public License.
